net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.platform.swing.builder.components

Class AbstractListComponentHandlerTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.platform.swing.builder.components.AbstractListComponentHandlerTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractComboBoxComponentHandlerTest, AbstractListBoxComponentHandlerTest

    public abstract class AbstractListComponentHandlerTest
extends Object
    A base test class for component handlers dealing with list-like components. This class already implements some tests related to manipulations of the internally used list model. Concrete sub classes must provide a reference to a concrete handler implementation.
    Version:
    $Id: AbstractListComponentHandlerTest.java 205 2012-01-29 18:29:57Z oheger $
    Author:
    Oliver Heger
